AssertionError: Wrong status code, Actual: '403', expected 401
assert 403 == 401
 +  where 403 = <Response [403]>.status_code
 +  and   401 = <lookup 'status_codes'>.unauthorized
 +    where <lookup 'status_codes'> = <module 'requests.status_codes' from '/usr/local/lib/python3.12/site-packages/requests/status_codes.py'>.codes
 +      where <module 'requests.status_codes' from '/usr/local/lib/python3.12/site-packages/requests/status_codes.py'> = requests.status_codes
